---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About">
  <header>
    <h1>
      Hi, I'm Kade,{" "}
      <strike class="text-strike">
        a <strong>Designer with a passion for Cybersecurity.</strong>
      </strike>{" "}
      a<strong> Human Being.</strong>
    </h1>
  </header>

  <main>
    <div>
      <p>
        My work is dedicated to designing thoughtful experiences. This means
        that I ask questions, brainstorm, plan approaches, and build enduring
        solutions.
      </p>
      <p>
        My introduction to design came at a young age with strong ambitions to
        learn and create high-quality work. Over the years, these ambitions
        continue to drive my projects as I look forward to continuous growth.
      </p>
      <p>
        Apart from design work, I enjoy coding, exercising, video games, my cat,
        and learning American Sign Language!
      </p>
      <p>
        I’m currently exploring new opportunities and available for freelance.
        I'd love to hear from you — hi@kadezaccaro.com.
      </p>
    </div>

    <section>
      <header>
        <h2>Education & Certifications</h2>
      </header>

      <div class="achievements">
        <div class="achievement-card">
          <h4>Associate's Degree in Cybersecurity</h4>
          <p>Lanier Technical College &mdash; December 2026</p>
        </div>

        <div class="achievement-card">
          <h4>CompTIA A+ Certification</h4>
          <p>CompTIA &mdash; May 2026</p>
        </div>

        <div class="achievement-card">
          <h4>CompTIA Security+ Certification</h4>
          <p>CompTIA &mdash; June 2026</p>
        </div>

        <div class="achievement-card">
          <h4>CompTIA Network+ Certification</h4>
          <p>CompTIA &mdash; July 2026</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="header-section skills">
      <h2>Skills & Expertise</h2>
      <div class="skills-grid">
        <div class="skill-card">
          <h3>Network Security</h3>
          <p>Firewalls, IDS/IPS, VPN, Threat Detection</p>
          <p>
            I'm currently pursuing a degree in Cybersecurity, and aiming for
            CompTIA certifications along the way.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="skill-card">
          <h3>Penetration Testing</h3>
          <p>OWASP, Burp Suite, Metasploit, Kali Linux</p>
        </div>
        <div class="skill-card">
          <h3>Incident Response</h3>
          <p>Forensics, Log Analysis, Security Audits</p>
        </div>
        <div class="skill-card">
          <h3>Compliance</h3>
          <p>GDPR, HIPAA, ISO 27001, SOC 2</p>
        </div>
        <p>
          Proficient in HTML, CSS, JavaScript Experience with graphic and web
          design and UX principles Strong understanding of cybersecurity
          fundamentals Passionate about learning new technologies and staying
          updated Skilled at problem-solving and critical thinking
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
